I am a Lighting Designer, and Audio Engineer with over eight years of experience bridging the gap between ambitious creative visions and flawless live execution. My work spans theatrical productions, club environments, and festival stages.

I specialize in designing stage environments where lighting, audio, and decor operate in perfect collaboration.

Currently serving as a House Technician at Madam Amsterdam, I continue to push the technical possibilities  of live events, ensuring that every performance—from intimate plays to high-octane DJ sets—is an unforgettable experience.
